---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="support-content">
    <h1>App Support & FAQ</h1>

    <div class="faq-section">
      <details>
        <summary>How do I join D2?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          D2 is an invite-only platform. You’ll need an invite from an existing
          member or you can request access on our Join the Club page. Once
          approved, you’ll receive an invite link to create your account.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How does D2 track my steps?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          D2 syncs with your mobile device or compatible smartwatch to track
          your daily step count. Grant the app permission to read your step
          data, and D2 will update your progress on the leaderboard each day.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How do I connect my gaming account?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          Go to Settings in the D2 App and select "Connect Account." Follow the
          prompts to authenticate with Roblox or other supported platforms. We
          only collect and store your gaming account ID to provide in-game
          rewards.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>What rewards can I earn in D2?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          D2 offers in-game items, cosmetics, and Buffs (temporary perks in
          partner games). Unlock these rewards by reaching your daily step goals
          and maintaining streaks. Visit the Loot page in-app to see available
          rewards.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Do you store my personal information?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          We collect only your email address and gaming account ID for
          verification and rewards. We do not store your name, phone number, or
          location data. For more details, visit our <a
            href="privacy-policy.html">Privacy Policy</a
          >.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Can I delete my account and data?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          Yes. You can request account deletion in the Settings section of the
          app or by emailing <a href="mailto:support@d2health.club"
            >support@d2health.club</a
          >. Once deleted, your data will be removed unless required by law to
          be retained in anonymized form.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How do I reset my password?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          Authentication is handled via Supabase or your chosen login provider
          (e.g., Apple, Discord, Roblox). Use the "Forgot Password" link on the
          login screen to reset your password.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Does the app track analytics or location data?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          No, D2 does not collect analytics like screen views or location data.
          Only anonymized, aggregated data (e.g., total community steps) may be
          used for insights and improvements.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How secure is my data?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          We use industry-standard encryption and security protocols through our
          database provider, Supabase. Only authorized team members have access
          to limited user data.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Who can I contact for support?</summary>
        <div class="answer">
          If you need assistance, email us at <a
            href="mailto:support@d2health.club">support@d2health.club</a
          >. For privacy concerns, check our <a href="privacy-policy.html"
            >Privacy Policy</a
          >.
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
      <h2>Need more help?</h2>
      <p>
        Email us at <a href="mailto:support@d2health.club"
          >support@d2health.club</a
        >. We’re here to support your journey with D2!
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:support@d2health.club" class="cta-button"
        >Contact Support</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
